reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Polston, Nichelle. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.nbcphiladelphia.com/news/local/Del-Child-Sexual-Abuse-Case-Involving-DuPont-Heir-Resurfaces-250874101.html\">\"Sexual Abuse Case Involving Du Pont Heir Resurfaces\"</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2015-05-15</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Sexual+Abuse+Case+Involving+Du+Pont+Heir+Resurfaces&amp;rft.aulast=Polston&amp;rft.aufirst=Nichelle&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcphiladelphia.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2FDel-Child-Sexual-Abuse-Case-Involving-DuPont-Heir-Resurfaces-250874101.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATrial+and+sentencing+of+Robert+H.+Richards+IV\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Barrish, Cris (March 19, 2014). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/local/2014/03/18/du-pont-heir-faces-child-sex-lawsuit/6565107/\">\"Du Pont heir faces child sex lawsuit\"</a>. <i>The News Journal</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">May 15,</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=The+News+Journal&amp;rft.atitle=Du+Pont+heir+faces+child+sex+lawsuit&amp;rft.date=2014-03-19&amp;rft.aulast=Barrish&amp;rft.aufirst=Cris&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.delawareonline.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2014%2F03%2F18%2Fdu-pont-heir-faces-child-sex-lawsuit%2F6565107%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATrial+and+sentencing+of+Robert+H.+Richards+IV\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&